Subject: Still Interested in the [job_title] Role? Let's Connect!

Body:
<html><body style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #222222; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
<p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0;">Hi <strong>[applicant_first_name]</strong>,</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0;">I hope you're doing well. We wanted to check in and see if you're still interested in the <strong>[job_title]</strong> role with Outsourced Pro Global.</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0;">Your application caught our attention, and we believe your skills and experience align well with what we're looking for. We're excited about the possibility of you joining our team.</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0;">If you'd like to move forward, simply schedule an interview at a time that works best for you using the link below:</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0;"><a href="[Schedule Your Interview Here]" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #0057b8; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px;">Schedule Your Interview</a></p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0;">Should you have any concerns or questions, please email, call, or text your Recruitment Specialist: [recruiter_phone_line]</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0;">Thank you for considering Outsourced Pro Global as your next career step. We look forward to connecting with you soon.</p>

[signature]
</body></html>
